awards.text: Nominated for 2 Primetime Emmys. Another 2 wins & 2 nominations.

fullplot: The smart, sassy actress/comedienne's third solo HBO special features material taped in front of a live audience at NYC's Beacon Theater. In this show, Ellen makes her triumphant return to the irreverent, irresistible humor that launched her career.
